commitResults.messageBody:
This commit introduces the Expense, Budget, BudgetManager, and
InputManager classes for managing budgets and expenses.

- Expense: Tracks expenses with description, and amount.
- Budget: Creates budgets with categories and optional limits, and
  tracks expenses.
- BudgetManager: Manages multiple budgets and assigns expenses to
  specific categories.
- InputManager: Handles user input, validates commands, and interacts
  with BudgetManager.

Error handling and Javadoc documentation have been added. Basic test
cases for Expense class are included.
